## Value Export

By default, when working with exporters such as [CSV Export](./csv-export/) or [Excel Export](./excel-export/), the value of the Row Header Column is not exported. 
This behaviour can be changed by toggling the `exportRowHeaderColumn` of the export params.

```{% frameworkTransform=true %}
const gridOptions = {
    enableRowHeaderColumn: true,
    cellSelection: true,
    defaultExcelExportParams: {
        exportRowHeaderColumn: true,
    },
}
```

